  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gun recovered from army soldier in anti-government protest",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A gun stolen from an army soldier during an anti-government protest near Parliament on July 13 has been recovered by the navy.",
        "Police said that during the demonstration near Poltua Junction, Pattaramullai, the protesters attacked an army soldier and stole a T-56 rifle and some bullets.",
        "In this case, last Saturday (23) the Navy divers also recovered guns and empty magazines from under the Thiavannawa Bridge.",
        "Subsequently, the gun and the empty magazine have been handed over to the Welikada police and further investigations are being conducted."
      ],
